# Client environment variables
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL defines the base URL used by the frontend when
# issuing API requests.  If not set, the app defaults to `/api`, which
# is convenient for local development when a Vite dev server proxy is
# forwarding requests to the backend.
#
# When the server is deployed separately (for example to Render), set
# this variable to the full URL of the backend service:
#
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://my-backend-on-render.onrender.com
